			<div class="content" id="post-content-1494607">
									

<p>That just reinforces how bland this thing is. Without outside guessing on who gets assigned to it it's just a duck pond, it serves the same purpose as a vacation for people who work on shitty SCPs (not shitty in quality.)</p>
<p>All of that aside, look at it, it's a peaceful pond that makes people feel better because it's relaxing. How was it discovered? Who came across it and was so utterly shaken with it's niceness that they decided it must be beyond the constraints of normalcy?</p>
<p>&quot;Oh man, I'm so depressed and I hate my job&#8230;. This is a nice duck pond, it's so calming and relaxing&#8230; I can just feel my troubles melting away&#8230; Wait&#8230; No&#8230;. NO NO NO! It's too relaxing! I have to call the cops! Oh jeez, this is going to change the world!&quot;</p>

