			<div class="content" id="post-content-1494636">
									

<p>Yeah, see how the article doesn't state anything about justification for murder? There isn't even a tiny hint/trace of this thing doing more than making people feel good.</p>
<p>One again, the article itself is boring and uninteresting because it needs outside theories to make it more than a feel-good pond with ducks. I'm not saying it needs to be grimdark at all to be interesting, it could be interesting without any horror being implied, but this isn't it.</p>
<p>If an article needs speculation to be even remotely interesting then it's doing something wrong.</p>

